  "title": "ISic001528. I.Sicily inscription 001528",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ἐνθάδε κῖτε <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πολυχ\n                    ρόνιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πολυχ\n                    ρόνιος\">Πολυχ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ρόνιος</span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σεραπία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σεραπία\">Σεραπία</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>Ἠγόρασεν τῷ τότ-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ε καιρῷ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πολυχρονίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πολυχρονίου\">Πολυχρονίου</span></span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>αἱ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σεραπία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σεραπία\">Σεραπία</span></span> ἐπὶ τῷ κυρί-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ῳ μου ἐπισκόπῳ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Συρα\n                    κοσίῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Συρα\n                    κοσίῳ\">Συρα-<br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>κοσίῳ</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span clas